    "This integration is imperative because the reward functions, which drive workflow development, must originate from human objectives and goals.",
    "Additionally, humans can collaborate with AI in refining hypotheses and recognizing serendipitous experimental findings, a partnership that helps mitigate potential misalignments between ML-generated workflows and human intentions.",
